name: Aditi
description: Large 1 bedroom in the heart of River North. Beautiful open kitchen with granite countertops and breakfast bar. Hardwood Floors, in unit washer/dryer, lots of closet space & extra storage. Large private balcony with south views! Premiere building has 24hr door staff, elevator, exercise room, party room, and roofdeck.

name: Mishra
description: Spacious split-level townhome at the entrance to Hawaii Kai with easy access to the highway. Master bedroom includes a spacious loft that could be a great office or storage space. Crescent West is a pet friendly community and includes 2 assigned parking stalls (one covered and one open). The heart of Hawaii Kai shopping and dining is minutes away as is the beach and Koko Head Crater. Access the bus lines steps away from the home for a quick commute into town. Guests will enjoy the plentiful street parking right out front.
